edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.defecttracker.models.validators

Class DefectValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.cs.wpisuitetng.modules.defecttracker.models.validators.DefectValidator

  • public class DefectValidator
extends java.lang.Object
    Validates Defects so that they fit in with the given Data implementation. Note that Data could be something used client-side (e.g. a wrapper around a local cache of Users so you can check assignee usernames as-you-type).
